OL,3,CMan jailed for attempting to kidnap
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old as he slept
OL,6,FIt was four o'clock in the morning
OL,7,Fwhen the child's mother woke to find a
OL,8,Fman at the end of her bed, holding her
OL,9,Ftwo-year-old son in his arms.
OL,11,FUpon being disturbed, he dropped the
OL,12,Fchild and ran out of the house.
OL,14,FReece Jolliffe, 28, of Amesbury
OL,15,Fentered the victim's home through an
OL,16,Funlocked door at around 4am on
OL,17,FSeptember 2, 2023. He'd been drinking
OL,18,Fheavily.
