OL,3,CMan jailed for attempting to kidnap
OL,4,Ctwo-year-old as he slept
OL,6,FPolice officers went to Jolliffe's
OL,7,Fhome address and arrested him on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of kidnap.
OL,10,FDuring interview, Jolliffe claimed he
OL,11,Fcould not remember what happened after
OL,12,Fhe left the pub he had been drinking
OL,13,Fat.
OL,15,FJolliffe was given an immediate two-
OL,16,Fyear custodial sentence and a 10-year
OL,17,Frestraining order was imposed to
OL,18,Fprevent him from contacting the
OL,19,Fvictim's family and attending their
OL,20,Fhome address.
