OL,4,Ctwo-year-old as he slept
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to attempted kidnap
OL,7,Fand was sentenced to two years
OL,8,Fimprisonment at Salisbury Crown Court.
OL,10,FSgt Matthew Goldring said: "This was a
OL,11,Fdeeply disturbing incident for the
OL,12,Fentire family.
OL,14,F"We do not know Jolliffe's full
OL,15,Fintentions when he entered the
OL,16,Fvictim's home, but his actions were
OL,17,Fsignificantly alarming."
